🗨️ CHAT
All of your messages, except for any commands, will go to all of the members

You can remove yourself from the chat by texting

#{bold('#stop')}
sms:%{channel_phone_number}?body=#stop

---

👥 MANAGE PEOPLE
Add more people or groups by texting #{bold('#add')} along with their names

#{bold('#add @nameone, name two, and group three')}
sms:%{channel_phone_number}?body=#add·

Remove people by texting #{bold('#remove')} with their names

#{bold('#remove @nameone, name two, and group three')}
sms:%{channel_phone_number}?body=#remove·

You can see everyone who is a member:

#{bold('#list')}
sms:%{root_phone_number}?body=#list

